[size=6][b][color=Gray]PILLAGERS AND MORE GREAT FEATURES NOW IN BETA![/color]
掠夺者以及很多新特性进入 Beta 测试阶段！[/b][/size]

[size=4][color=Gray]Available in betas on Xbox One, Windows 10 and Android![/color]
在 Xbox One、Windows 10 和安卓设备上可用！[/size][/align]

[size=3][color=Gray]Have you tried playing a Minecraft beta? It's where we test upcoming features of the game! To try these features, you have to play a version of Minecraft that supports betas (so that's the Windows 10, Xbox One and Android versions). You can see how to sign up for a Minecraft beta on each version here. You can also find more help regarding this specific beta on our feedback site.[/color]
你试过 Minecraft beta 吗？我们在 beta 中测试游戏的新特性！如果你想尝试这些新特性，你需要玩支持 beta 的 Minecraft 版本（即 Windows 10、Xbox One 以及安卓版）。[url=https://minecraft.net/article/how-get-minecraft-betas]你可以在这里看到适用于不同版本的注册 Minecraft beta 的方法（英文页面）。[/url]你也可以在[url=https://feedback.minecraft.net/hc/en-us/articles/360019773811]我们的反馈网站（英文）[/url]中找到更多有关 beta 的帮助。[/size]

[size=3][color=Gray]Remember, beta features can be unstable – the whole reason we want players trying them this early is to give us feedback and catch bugs for us to fix – so backup your worlds! We've added loads of new stuff to for the 1.9.0.0 beta, so we thought we'd update this article with all the new features you can try, like Pillagers, Bamboo, new flowers and tons of new stairs and slabs! For a full list of changes and fixes, as well as a great place to give us feedback about the beta, head to our feedback site.[/color]
beta 特性可能不稳定——我们让玩家提前尝试这些特性的主要原因就是为了给我们反馈以及找出并修复崩溃漏洞——所以记得备份你的世界！我们为 1.9.0.0 beta 加入了很多新东西，所以我们在这篇文章中更新了所有你可以尝试的新特性，比如掠夺者、竹子、新的花朵和很多新楼梯新台阶！想要查看更改和修复的完整列表，以及给予我们有关 beta 的反馈，请到我们的[url=https://feedback.minecraft.net/hc/en-us/articles/360019773811]反馈网站[/url][/size]

