[size=5][b][color=Gray]PARTICLE EFFECTS AND ANIMATION ADD-ONS[/color]
粒子和动画 ADD-ON[/b][/size]

[size=3][color=Gray]Not familiar with add-ons? They're a fantastic way to bring even greater levels of customisation to all editions of Minecraft. You can learn more about them here![/color]
不熟悉 add-on？它们是对任何版本（译注：指任何基岩版）的 Minecraft 进行极自由的自定义的方式。[url=https://minecraft.net/en-us/addons/]你可以在这里了解更多（英文页面）。[/url][/size]

[size=3][color=Gray]Previously, add-ons only allowed you to modify existing mobs in the game, but with New Entities you can add more mobs. You can use Data Driven Spawning to control which mobs spawn in your worlds. Animations will give you more customisation options, so you’ll be able to craft the horrifying eight-legged mob of your dreams/our nightmares. Particles will let you pretty up your mobs with cool effects.[/color]
以前，add-on 只允许你修改游戏中现存的生物，不过有了[b]添加实体[/b]这一功能，你可以添加更多生物了。你可以使用[b]数据驱动生成[/b]来控制那些生物可以在你的世界里面生成。[b]动画[/b]给了你更多的自定义选项，所以你可以制作恐怖的八条腿的生物来实现你的梦想/我们的噩梦。[b]粒子[/b]允许你能通过添加很酷的效果来美化你的生物。[/size]

[size=3][color=Gray]These options are now in the beta, but we've also added resource and behaviour packs that you can download to access some special example mobs we showed off at MINECON Earth! Are they as cute and cuddly as the cats and pandas? Er... well...[/color]
尽管这些选项现在仍处于 beta 阶段，我们提供了一套资源包和行为包，你可以下载它们并查看我们在 MINECON Earth 上展示的一些特殊的生物例子！它们是否和猫和熊猫一样可爱呢？嗯…啊…[/size]

