[size=3][color=Gray]First of all, make sure you're signed up for the beta. You'll be able to tell because the word 'Beta!' will be in large yellow text below the title on the main menu. In the smaller white text along the top, it'll tell you which beta you're signed up for. Make sure it says 'beta 1.8.0.8'. Use this link if you need more help![/color]
首先，确保你注册了 beta。你可以通过看主界面上有没有大黄字「Beta!」来得知你是否成功注册了。顶部的小白字显示了你所注册的 beta 版本，确保它是「beta 1.8.0.8」。[url=https://feedback.minecraft.net/hc/en-us/articles/360016529492-Minecraft-Beta-1-8-0-8-Xbox-One-Windows-10-Android-]如果你需要帮助，看看这个链接（英文）[/url][/size]

[img=768,432]http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/0065mBHhly1fxfw5ymcnqj30lc0c0zta.jpg[/img]

[size=3][color=Gray]Then you'll need to run these two files:[/color]
然后你需要运行这两个文件：[/size]

[url=https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/ca31e3a89a6324e28091a3ec87564e07-minecon_behaviors.mcpack]MINECON 2018 添加实体示例行为包[/url]

[url=https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/65c018b48b5d5922a8a62241195e1ed7-minecon_resources.mcpack]MINECON 2018 添加实体示例资源包[/url]

[size=3][color=Gray]These are .McWorld files which means you can just select 'run' and they'll open Minecraft on your device and start importing into it. You'll see a screen like this:[/color]
这些都是 [b].McWorld[/b] 文件，你可以直接「运行」，它们会自动打开你的设备上的 Minecraft 并开始导入。你会看到一个类似这样的界面：[/size]

[img=768,432]http://wx4.sinaimg.cn/large/0065mBHhly1fxfwabo0tjj30lc0c0wlv.jpg[/img]
[1/2] - 你会看到在屏幕上方有「正在导入关卡」，然后很快变为…

[img=768,432]http://wx3.sinaimg.cn/large/0065mBHhly1fxfwac8u01j30lc0c0gst.jpg[/img]
[2/2] - 「关卡导入成功。」棒！

[size=3][color=Gray]Next, you'll need to download these two files:[/color]
接下来，你需要下载这两个文件：[/size]

[url=https://aka.ms/MinecraftBetaResources]BETA 资源包文件（1.8.0-BETA1）[/url]（译注：原文给的链接是错的）

[url=https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/e55a6f93f33b40b045f8d592427b60fd-Vanilla_Behavior_Pack_1.8.0_Beta1.zip]BETA 行为包文件（1.8.0-BETA1）[/url]

[size=3][color=Gray]They're .zip files. Once they've downloaded, rename the files – you want to change the file extension from .zip to .McWorld[/color]
这些是 [b].zip[/b] 文件。下载完成以后，重命名这些文件——把文件后缀从 [b].zip[/b] 改成 [b].McWorld[/b]

[color=Gray]Once you've done that, open the file and it should automatically import into Minecraft.[/color]
在你做完这件事以后，打开文件，它应该会自动导入到 Minecraft。[/size]

[img=748,536]https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/styles/small/s3/04c173a1ebf7c2a2c33bdc651c169755-GuideA.JPEG[/img]
[1/4] - 点了上面的链接以后，你会看到这个。点「OK」。

[img=748,421]https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/styles/small/s3/828186142a6edb373c7d5ecf7fd8359d-GuideB.JPEG[/img]
[2/4] - 下载好了以后，你有了一个需要被重命名的 .zip 文件。为什么我没有一个更有趣的桌面背景？[b]因为我忙着做这个教程[/b]。

[img=748,421]https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/styles/small/s3/eed6ea2ece640e27911f61c88f93567b-GuideC.jpeg[/img]
[3/4] - 将文件后缀从 .zip 改成 .McWorld。你会看到这个询问你「确实要更改吗」的窗口。我们当然确定了！继续点「是」。

[img=748,421]https://community-content-assets.minecraft.net/upload/styles/small/s3/4e7cc88241341d27eb049ad190047983-GuideD.JPEG[/img]
[4/4] - 假设你拼对了 .McWorld，然后你会发现这个文件的图标从无聊的米色文件夹变成了漂亮的 Minecraft 方块！继续双击它并把它导入到你的 Minecraft beta。

